{
  "stem": "7860.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't come from a religious home, but one thing I knew, somehow instinct to, Shema Adonai Eloheinu Shema Israel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I kept saying over and over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I heard a woman being interrogated in front of my bookcase, being accused she's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the people with her kept saying, no, she's not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They know her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I fell asleep from fear alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I fell asleep thinking, I'm dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I didn't want to see myself dying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When I woke up, everything was moving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Trains were going all different directions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I climbed up from behind the bookcase and continued my journey riding the trains back and forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And another incident happened to other people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In Warsaw, Warsaw had three main railroad-- railroad stations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH], it means the main depot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH], which means the Western.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And Praga-- three railroad-- [INAUDIBLE] on the main railroad depot in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the Germans used to capture Poles, and put them on trucks and send them up to forced labor camps to Germany, because they needed manpower.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And any Poles that made the wrong move, they'd shoot them right on sight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There were 14, 15-year-olds, it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the same Poles-- I couldn't believe myself-- would capture a Jew and turn him over to the Germans at the same moment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they would round up, and circle, and surround the station, let's say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And grab the Poles and they would put them on-- on tracks and send them off to Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I would figure I would like to offer myself to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But one, I was too young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Second, I had to go for a physical checkup, I was told.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I'm circumcised.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Nobody told me this but I somehow overheard, and you're learning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "You become like a busybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
